    "description": {
      "value": "<strong>Bloodrager - Bloodline Powers</strong><br/><br/><p>At 20th level, you can summon a ghostly army from a fallen civilization once per day. This functions as spiritual ally with a caster level equal to your level, except that it summons a number of allies equal to your Constitution modifier, and the allies use your Strength modifier for attack rolls. You can direct all of these allies with a single swift action. Each ally can attack a different target or the same target, as you direct. The allies remain until the spell's duration ends or your bloodrage ends, whichever comes first.</p>",
